Corporate & Other


	Ergon, Inc., provides centralized management and administrative services to all operating companies and maintains certain investments and activities not directly associated with ongoing Ergon subsidiary operations. Administrative Services
	To ensure consistency in the quality and integrity of its global operations, Ergon, Inc., provides various administrative services to its operating divisions and subsidiaries from its corporate office in Jackson, Mississippi.
	These administrative services include accounting, business process management, communications, credit, customer service, engineering, environmental health & safety, finance, human resources, information technology, internal audit, logistics, procurement, risk management, supply and distribution, tax, training, travel and treasury.
	Ergon Securities, Inc., provides specialized financing options to the consolidated subsidiaries. 










